videos.description: In transition, De'Aaron Fox flips the ball back to Malik Monk who shoots  a three that bounces around the rim before finally dropping in.
videos.headline: Monk gets generous bounce on 3-pointer

videos.description: Kentucky swings the ball around the perimeter, eventually getting it to Dominique Hawkins who drains the three.
videos.headline: Great ball movement leads to a Kentucky 3-pointer

videos.description: Off a missed shot, Edrice Adebayo follows and slams the rebound in with two hands.
videos.headline: Adebayo sends it in with power

videos.description: Kentucky moves the ball around, eventually finding De'Aaron Fox who drives, scores, and draws a foul.
videos.headline: Great passing allows Fox to score and draw the foul

videos.description: Kentucky's Malik Monk drives, dishes behind him for Edrice Adebayo who catches and slams.
videos.headline: Great pass from Monk sets up an Adebayo slam

videos.description: Dominique Hawkins drives and passes to an open Derek Willis who drains a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Kentucky hits 10th 3-pointer of the first half on a Willis triple

videos.description: Kentucky's Isaiah Briscoe attacks, spins in the lane, then scores and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Nifty spin move from Briscoe allows him to score

videos.description: De'Aaron Fox steals a pass, up court he lobs for Derek Willis who catches and slams.
videos.headline: Fox steal leads to huge alley-oop

videos.description: Kentucky head coach John Calipari and Malik Monk on the team's 83-58 win over Tennessee
videos.headline: Kentucky head coach John Calipari and Malik Monk on the team's 83-58 win over Tennessee

videos.description: Malik Monk scores 20 points and grabs 8 rebounds in a decisive win over the Volunteers.
videos.headline: Kentucky dominates Tennessee 83-58
